result.name: 天天Plus海南雞飯 (銅鑼灣店)

reviews.text:
The waiter take our order and guide us thru the process of choosing food. He inform us if the food is one of there best seller or not. 

After awhile the food started to come out. It is faster than the usual wait of any restaurant. The food is great. 

Restaurant environment is nice. I find it a little darker.

Edit: 2019 March 30
I come back here for the 4 times already,  very consistent cook and it is really good. The lady that takes care of our order and served our food is Olivia. She is very very good in Service. Efficient,  Quick, friendly and respectful. My wife appreciate her services.

No matter how good the food at this place is the wait of 25 mins for a 2 person table is just unreasonable and the receptionist seems uninterested in her job but would rather wait tables so people waiting outside even when there are tables available inside.
In hong kong this is high class restaurant but just the local friendly food in singapore
Best service food is delicous... Too bad they got rid of ths cha sui

The ingredients for the dishes were of good quality, I particularly liked the Vegetables in Chicken Sauce and the Deep Fried Bean Curd with Cereal and Mince Garlic. The Tian Tian Hainanese rice came along with a nice surprise in the form of a sweet sauce, served with cucumbers to break apart it's tartness. However, I would like to point out that the chicken meat had turned bad, I would say that it was most likely because of the freezer not being cold enough. I would suggest that you correct this error immediately, since this happens to be your main selling point.

Thank you.

reviews.text: 可話不好食，但又真不能話好食🤔🤔

去到門前燈光黑沉沉本來我都覺得沒有太大驚起！但當服務生帶我們進入餐廳後就發現餐廳內的裝修格調很別樹風格，杯杯碟碟配上懷舊的花紋襯托時尚的餐具，帶有時尚感易保留經典的味道！

職員很快就拿餐牌過來招待我們，介紹他們的招牌菜，又拿到獎的米芝蓮菜式和簡單介紹各式各樣新加坡風味菜式給我們！最後我們很快就點了3個菜2杯特飲和2個特色豆腐花

天天海南雞 $148
份量十足海南雞 幼滑細嫩 雞汁入味，還有爽脆的青瓜襯托

海南印象 $88
其實是由幾款蔬菜再用粉絲做底的雜菜煲, 用了秘製的煮法醬汁滲入了粉絲內變得更惹味

筋腩相逢$98
牛筋加牛腩兩者煮得非常好，牛腩咬下去非常鬆軟不會有煙韌感覺..而牛筋質感非常軟淋淋入口即溶，配合秘製的醬汁令到整個煲變得味道更加昇華

Under Up $68
用牛奶樽裝起的青綠色特飲 有紅莓子和藍莓，味道似益力多！ 適合任何年齡朋友

Grown Up $68
青瓜配上檸檬汁, 清新開胃！這個配搭就是東南亞的特飲

天天特色豆腐花
聽侍應說這個天天特色豆腐花是新加坡廚師秘製用了杏仁來配製，杏仁味勁重！豆腐花質地本身超綿超滑
海南雞飯一般，肉質算滑但雞味淡，海蜇頭較碎及唔夠脆口。雞飯不值此價格，食味還不如大家樂及美心一般茶餐廳，只是坐得較好及不用自己取餐。

reviews.text: One of the most upscale shopping mall in Kowloon. Conceirge service is good, parking friendly. Always clean and food ventilation. Washrooms are of top quality, would be great if they can add some cultural related stores like bookstores for people to grab brain food. Cinema is also comfortable

THE shopping mall in Hong Kong, with huge size, a great variety of brands (particularly in the luxury segment) and even five different themes for different areas based on the ancient Chinese elements. Good variety of food offerings as well, with plenty of hotels and transport nearby whether you prefer trains, subway, buses or taxi. The mall is new and fresh, and the overall area is very nice should you decide to take a walk nearby.
Very clean shopping mall with beautiful aesthetics. The shops were nice, and the restaurants were also nice. Definitely would recommend to tourists and travellers.
Nice place. Beautiful displays and products.  Well lit. Friendly staff. I didnt buy anything but very nice store.
Instructions inside the mall aren't clear, you have to go round and round. Shops are big but like a one way route, take you long time to get back. Get a map before you visit.
